citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:20 to 11:50 a.m.
on 23 JAN 24.
Upon arrival at the facility I honked my horn and called the contact number provided but was unable to leave a message. I
then sent a text message to the contact number. I waited 30 minutes and departed.
End Section
